{"url": "https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-18076207", "text": "Britney Spears was the all-American pop princess who shot to superstardom in her teens before a very public breakdown. Now, her appointment as a judge on the US X Factor represents a full return to the media spotlight.\n\nThe most stark illustration of how far Britney Spears had fallen came on 16 February 2007 when, after she spent just 24 hours in a rehabilitation clinic, the paparazzi tracked her down to a Los Angeles tattoo parlour - and discovered she was completely bald.\n\nThe act of shaving her head was a clear rejection of her former persona and of her life as a pop starlet in the public gaze.\n\nHer meltdown came after eight years as the archetypal modern pop starlet - \"Miss American Dream since I was 17,\" as she put it in her 2007 single Piece of Me.", "images": ["https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/385/cpsprodpb/a5f9/live/a3666560-c514-11f0-b288-51552c83ad58.png", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/464/cpsprodpb/13985/production/_116916208_360395da-5196-4cfb-ace6-e853143959cc.jpg", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/464/cpsprodpb/2BFD/production/_116916211_2d4a9754-78ae-4120-a817-2dc5b008e631.jpg", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/226/cpsprodpb/A12D/production/_116916214_b8218021-fa71-4a6e-a959-ddc63a13fc4c.jpg", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/480/cpsprodpb/e070/live/0f8ea1f0-c540-11f0-b288-51552c83ad58.jpg", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/385/cpsprodpb/9234/live/3aa10aa0-c530-11f0-89b2-992f173b35b9.jpg", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/464/cpsprodpb/16095/production/_116916209_1c541e4f-aaf6-46f6-a247-2815062eea1d.jpg", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/226/cpsprodpb/04ED/production/_116916210_af4537cc-8350-49e1-a2d3-155fd3f7a90e.jpg", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/385/cpsprodpb/56e3/live/1da5b0c0-c532-11f0-9839-6584ec7afe70.jpg", "https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/480/cpsprodpb/2050/live/cba5e0e0-c565-11f0-9fb5-5f3a3703a365.